 \tau_j^\natural(\Xi_k^{(i)}) = \sum a_{k\ell} \tau_j^\natural(\Xi_\ell^{(j)}) = \sum a_{k\ell} \xi_\ell^{(j)} = \xi_k^{(i)} = \tau_i^\natural(\Xi_k^{(i)}).
